355
00:32:11,420 --> 00:32:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] Pet minuta, ne više.

356
00:32:12,420 --> 00:32:13,420
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan i jan.

357
00:32:13,420 --> 00:32:14,420
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan i jan.

358
00:32:14,420 --> 00:32:21,420
[SPEAKER_01] S time da mi je fenomenalno rekla moja draga sestra u Kristu koja sa mnom blisko surađuje,

359
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:29,420
