361
00:32:35,420 --> 00:32:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znesla.

362
00:32:37,420 --> 00:32:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] Terapija kod njega.

363
00:32:39,420 --> 00:32:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] Onda recimo taj dio završi taj moj molitveni ujutro, idemo dalje, idemo poslije po klince,

364
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:49,420
