1150
01:30:16,600 --> 01:30:18,600
[SPEAKER_03] Plesao se po stolu u konobismo.

1151
01:30:18,600 --> 01:30:19,600
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

1152
01:30:19,600 --> 01:30:20,600
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

