1157
01:30:27,600 --> 01:30:28,600
[SPEAKER_03] A uopće je to tako bilo veselo.

1158
01:30:28,600 --> 01:30:29,600
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

1159
01:30:29,600 --> 01:30:30,600
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

1160
01:30:30,600 --> 01:30:31,600
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

1161
01:30:31,600 --> 01:30:32,600
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

1162
01:30:33,600 --> 01:30:34,600
[SPEAKER_03] Tako zapravo.

1163
01:30:34,600 --> 01:30:35,600
[SPEAKER_03] A nekim je to teško za prihvatiti.

1164
01:30:35,600 --> 01:30:39,600
[SPEAKER_03] Jer kao misle naš biti katolik, biti vijenik, to mora biti nešto strogo.

1165
01:30:39,600 --> 01:30:40,600
[SPEAKER_03] Nešto.

1166
01:30:40,600 --> 01:30:41,600
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, to su dobre teme uopće.

1167
01:30:41,600 --> 01:30:43,600
[SPEAKER_01] Jako dobre teme naše.

1168
01:30:43,600 --> 01:30:47,600
[SPEAKER_03] Na kraju kraja ono humor i zezancija.

1169
01:30:47,600 --> 01:30:48,600
[SPEAKER_03] Zdravi humor.

1170
01:30:48,600 --> 01:30:49,600
[SPEAKER_03] To je tako potrebno.

1171
01:30:49,600 --> 01:30:50,600
