1192
01:31:32,600 --> 01:31:34,600
[SPEAKER_01] E, ali izletiš, učiš.

1193
01:31:34,600 --> 01:31:35,600
[SPEAKER_01] Kužiš.

1194
01:31:35,600 --> 01:31:37,600
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da moram biti iskren.

1195
01:31:37,600 --> 01:31:39,600
