1196
01:31:39,600 --> 01:31:41,600
[SPEAKER_01] Pritisak je biti javna ličnost.

1197
01:31:41,600 --> 01:31:43,600
[SPEAKER_01] Podložan si rešetanju.

1198
01:31:43,600 --> 01:31:45,600
[SPEAKER_01] Podložan si rešetanju, da.

1199
01:31:45,600 --> 01:31:48,600
[SPEAKER_03] Kaže, budite mudri ko zmije i bezazleni poput golubova.

1200
01:31:48,600 --> 01:31:49,600
