1202
01:31:51,600 --> 01:31:53,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je vježba.

1203
01:31:53,600 --> 01:31:57,600
[SPEAKER_01] To je vježba, dugoživotna vježba.

1204
01:31:57,600 --> 01:32:04,600
[SPEAKER_03] Nekad si, to kad si govorio, sam još jedna stvar.

1205
01:32:04,600 --> 01:32:08,600
[SPEAKER_03] Nekad čovjek misli da će s tom nekakvom izjavati preko tajem poslanja.

1206
01:32:08,600 --> 01:32:11,600
[SPEAKER_03] Nekad, to sam jednak od sebe znam primijeti.

1207
01:32:11,600 --> 01:32:13,600
